<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Delete Account - Smart Occlusion</title>
<style>
body {
  margin: 0;
  font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
  background: #f1f5f9;
}
.container {
  max-width: 450px;
  margin: 80px auto;
  background: #ffffff;
  padding: 30px;
  border-radius: 15px;
  box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
  text-align: center;
}
h1 {
  color: #2563eb;
  font-size: 26px;
}
p {
  color: #475569;
  font-size: 14px;
}
input, textarea {
  width: 100%;
  padding: 12px;
  margin-top: 15px;
  border: 1px solid #cbd5e1;
  border-radius: 10px;
  font-size: 14px;
}
textarea {
  resize: none;
  height: 80px;
}
button {
  width: 100%;
  margin-top: 20px;
  padding: 12px;
  background: #ef4444;
  color: white;
  border: none;
  border-radius: 10px;
  font-size: 16px;
  cursor: pointer;
}
button:hover {
  background: #dc2626;
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">
<h1>Delete Your Smart Occlusion Account</h1>
<p>We're sorry to see you go. Please fill this form to request permanent account deletion.</p>

<input type="text" placeholder="Enter your full name">
<input type="email" placeholder="Enter your registered email">
<input type="text" placeholder="Registered phone number">
<textarea placeholder="Reason for leaving (optional)"></textarea>

<button>Delete My Account</button>
</div>

</body>
</html>
